  "instructions": [
    "In a large tagine or Dutch oven, heat the olive oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the chipotle peppers and cook for 1-2 minutes until fragrant.",
    "Add the Fernbrake-Gosari, cumin, coriander, salt, and garlic powder. Cook for 5 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add the lime juice and stir to combine.",
    "Continue to cook for an additional 10-12 minutes, or until the Fernbrake-Gosari is tender.",
    "Warm tortillas by wrapping them in a damp paper towel and microwaving for 20-30 seconds.",
    "Assemble the tacos by placing a portion of the Fernbrake-Gosari mixture onto a tortilla, followed by a sprinkle of cilantro and a sprinkle of cheese (if using).",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
  ],
